friendLines.title: Hello
friendLines.description: Diluc, of Mondstadt. Not interested in idle chit-chat. If you have things you want to get done, let me know.

friendLines.title: Chat: Relax
friendLines.description: Guess we can rest a bit.

friendLines.title: Chat: Knights of Favonius
friendLines.description: You should really bring the Knights of Favonius with you next time.

friendLines.title: Chat: Wine Guild
friendLines.description: I still have a lot to do at the Guild. How about you take a rest while I go back?

friendLines.title: Chat: Preparation
friendLines.description: We should prepare while we can, then make a preemptive strike against the enemy.

friendLines.title: Chat: Planning
friendLines.description: Let's take a moment to rest and plan our next move.

friendLines.title: Chat: Warning
friendLines.description: Every course of action has its risks. Be careful.

friendLines.title: When It Rains: Umbrella
friendLines.description: I don't need an umbrella, but you can use one if you need.

friendLines.title: When It Rains: Cleansing
friendLines.description: Rain... If only it could cleanse the corrupt souls of this world.

friendLines.title: When the Sun Is Out
friendLines.description: Listen, as long as you stick to your own path, it doesn't matter what Mother Nature throws at you.

friendLines.title: When the Wind Is Blowing
friendLines.description: Some use the wind's whistling to drown out the sound of their crimes.

friendLines.title: Good Morning
friendLines.description: No need for small talk. All that matters is that you were safe last night.

friendLines.title: Good Afternoon
friendLines.description: Would you like to try the secret menu?

friendLines.title: Good Evening
friendLines.description: Night has fallen.

friendLines.title: Good Night
friendLines.description: Alright, see you next time. I'll make sure you leave safely.

friendLines.title: About Diluc
friendLines.description: The legend of the "Darknight Hero"? An interesting rumor.

friendLines.title: About Us: Needs
friendLines.description: Just say the word if you need anything. For reimbursements, ask Elzer.

friendLines.title: About Us: Proof
friendLines.description: You have already proven your determination. Well then, it is now time for you to witness my resolve.

friendLines.title: About the Vision
friendLines.description: Visions are a light in the sea of darkness that surrounds those who have lost their way. But for those who have faith, they are little more than badges of conviction.

friendLines.title: Something to Share
friendLines.description: Occasionally I'll work the bar at Angel's Share. The tavern is known for being the center of information in Mondstadt.

friendLines.title: Interesting Things
friendLines.description: What? Why do you ask? ...It's an owl, quietly watching its prey from the darkness, waiting for the perfect moment to strike... Flawless.

friendLines.title: About Kaeya
friendLines.description: Kaeya? You can only trust half of what he says... at best.

friendLines.title: About Lisa
friendLines.description: I believe Lisa has the potential to become the most reliable of the knights. If she's willing.

friendLines.title: About Jean: Enemies
friendLines.description: Trifling matters can become Jean's greatest enemy.

friendLines.title: About Jean: Responsibilities
friendLines.description: Her unparalleled sense of responsibility is the sole reason why she still hasn't found her true calling.

friendLines.title: About Mona
friendLines.description: The land of Mondstadt, by the Anemo Archon's grace, is bountiful. I see no need for the harvest forecasts of astrologers.

friendLines.title: About Diona
friendLines.description: Diona's attitude towards me is... how should I put it? Rather rigid. I've yet to find the opportunity to speak with her properly. I'm not sure if it's an issue with my family line or— Oh? It's not? She simply despises alcohol? Huh... I never thought I'd come across another bartender like myself in Mondstadt.

friendLines.title: About Varka
friendLines.description: Grand Master Varka... While I understand his disposition, I can make no sense of his actions. ...I—I've said too much already. I've long since left the Knights of Favonius. Forget I said anything.

friendLines.title: About Eula
friendLines.description: Ah, yes... I've heard about her. She has her own convictions. Her determination to liberate herself from the shackles of her clan is praiseworthy. But, she's... joined the Knights of Favonius.

friendLines.title: More About Diluc: I
friendLines.description: You have business to attend to?

friendLines.title: More About Diluc: II
friendLines.description: Huh? Knights of Favonius? ...I have nothing to say about them. We have different views is all.

friendLines.title: More About Diluc: III
friendLines.description: It's been a long while since I played chess with anyone but my butler. I just so happen to have a moment. Care to play a round?

friendLines.title: More About Diluc: IV
friendLines.description: Checkmate! ...Still, it's been a while since someone tested me this much.

friendLines.title: More About Diluc: V
friendLines.description: Not bad. Be it chess or combat, you always seem to surprise me. Hm, working with you is quite the novelty. So... I look forward to continuing to work with you, partner.

friendLines.title: Diluc's Hobbies
friendLines.description: The artwork in the manor? It's not mine. It's a collection that belonged to my late father.

friendLines.title: Diluc's Troubles
friendLines.description: The darkness that seethes with evil, full of demons that must be vanquished, will take more than a blade to be torn asunder.

friendLines.title: Favorite Food
friendLines.description: You want to know what's in my glass? It's... grape juice. My drink of choice.

friendLines.title: Least Favorite Food
friendLines.description: I don't like alcohol. It's just... I don't like how it feels in my mouth...

friendLines.title: Receiving a Gift: I
friendLines.description: Exquisite. Unforgettable flavors.

friendLines.title: Receiving a Gift: II
friendLines.description: I can see the chef put their heart into this one. A fine dish.

friendLines.title: Receiving a Gift: III
friendLines.description: ...Umm, thanks.

friendLines.title: Birthday
friendLines.description: Happy birthday. This is an important day for you. So tell me, what is it you wish for? If it is within my power to bestow it upon you, I will give it my consideration.

friendLines.title: Feelings About Ascension: Intro
friendLines.description: Power is necessary if we are to meet our objectives.

friendLines.title: Feelings About Ascension: Building Up
friendLines.description:
What lies in wait for us? I rarely stop to think about it.
No matter what dares to stand in my way, I must press forward.

friendLines.title: Feelings About Ascension: Climax
friendLines.description:
I've become stronger... Though it is still not enough, I will always face the darkness.
For dawn to come, there must be those who dare to pierce the darkness with their light.

friendLines.title: Feelings About Ascension: Conclusion
friendLines.description: I used to believe... if I was to stamp out evil, I would have to walk alone in darkness. However, seeing your perseverance, I know I was wrong. Friend... I owe you my thanks.

actionLines.title: Opening Treasure Chest: III
actionLines.description: We'll need more where that came from.

actionLines.title: Fallen: II
actionLines.description: There can be no excuse... for defeat...
